name: Above pixel
description: This is a frame of a choreographic work that marked my career. "Above" was a work that actually led me to transition to the professional world. It is an instant in which I connect energetically with my friend, Narciso Sanchez, with the space in which the choreography is presented and the energies of the public to whom it is presented. I manipulated the color, the structure a bit, and I liked the result.
